{"tid":349311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭睇SM TOWN 曬SJ EXO後台大合照","createTime":"2017-08-06T12:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T13:35:43.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e856d9a41b13195dc621cf21fe596b05fccb1225","tid":349311,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"由香港電競音樂節主辦的SM TOWN Special Stage in Hong Kong昨晚於紅館圓滿結束。行政長官林鄭月娥昨晚亦有到場欣賞。<br />\n<br />\n今日特首於社交網站上載她昨晚走入後台與一眾韓星大合照的相片。站在照片中間的林鄭月娥，身旁有旅發局主席林建岳，男團Super Junior成員銀赫為特首揸機，特首身後有女團f(x)的Luna、SHINee的珉豪(Minho)、EXO的Suho、NCT 127的泰容及女團Red Velvet的Yeri。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥一次過與眾多韓星合照，粉絲紛紛留言表示「很葡萄」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3095886abf7859edc5f30cc91a8f1079ec277074","tid":349311,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170806/s00007/1502007511578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170806%2Fs00007%2F1502007511578&d=fXcoo2K8GYl0vMm88S1LmsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d5390db0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170806%2Fs00007%2F1502007511578&h=9ee3bd46\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170806/s00007/1502007511578</a>"},{"pid":"e8a6f74ed49c6672508484d27e337a25e3e5d7f4","tid":349311,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"好葡萄d韓星可以同林鄭BB影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e149c62b3ae99f0cfc9e80d93ae3a23a3219d7fe","tid":349311,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"有冇做"},{"pid":"334e90da4c64567982dcc1fa284f1222e900de81","tid":349311,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited